{
  "stem": "20142.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you are-- were not prepared to deal with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the most important thing is that I counted very exactly the passages or the additional arteries joining it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when I got to the final one, I knew that this is the place that I would be ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when I climbed out, it was not be easy to lift up for me this plate from the canal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow evidently people passing by outside had seen some movement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they lifted it up with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I crawled-- they pulled me out out of there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I close this up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I knew I was in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when I was in ghetto, it was about-- I would say about 200 yards from the junction of [INAUDIBLE] and-- and Zamenhof.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But already on the Jew-- on the ghetto side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was today where there is a monument standing to the heroes of the Warsaw ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a place where the Jewish community of the small ghetto was existing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not far away from there was a street called Wolynska, spelled W-O-L-Y-N-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where I got out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Between that little place and [INAUDIBLE] was the street Wolynska.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was three days before-- [BACKROUND NOISE] be three days before Christmas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was on the 21st or 22nd of December of 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some people from the organization for the movement recognized me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, where did you come from?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say, I can't talk to nobody else but [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They said, why do you want to see [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I explained to them that it's very important.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm back from Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they heard Majdanek, they put the warm-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SIGHS] sort of caftans over me.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
